ibbt.sumo.sampleevaluators.datasets
Class DatasetSampleEvaluator

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
SampleEvaluator
Direct Known Subclasses:
GriddedDatasetSampleEvaluator, ScatteredDatasetSampleEvaluator
public abstract class DatasetSampleEvaluator
extends AbstractSampleQueueManager
implements SampleEvaluator

This class implements a dataset lookup sample evaluator. When given a sample point, this evaluator looks in a table for a simulation of a point as close to the given point as possible. It returns the output parameters at the closest point, and changes the input parameters to match the closest point that was used.

addToInputQueue

public void addToInputQueue(EvaluationUnit unit)
Since this class uses a data file to evaluate points this method immediately evaluates the incoming unit and puts it back on the evaluated queue. We do this since we assume such a dataset lookup is fast, thus blocking is permitted.
